plmMSA
======

This repository is a clean rebase and evolution of PLMAlign:

  https://github.com/DeepFoldProtein/PLMAlign

PLMAlign itself builds on PLMSearch (Liu et al., Nat. Commun. 15, 2775, 2024)
and incorporates ideas from pLM-BLAST and deepblast. Portions of the original
PLMAlign codebase are licensed under the MIT License with the following
copyrights:

  Copyright (c) 2023 Wei Liu
  Copyright (c) 2022 Laboratory of Structural Bioinformatics

Model weights loaded by plmMSA are distributed by their respective authors
under their own license terms, which apply independently of this repository:

  - Ankh and Ankh-Large (ElnaggarLab)  ..... Apache License 2.0
  - ESM1b (Meta AI / facebookresearch/esm)  MIT License
  - ProtT5 (Rostlab)  .......................custom RostLab license

Users are responsible for complying with the terms of each weight license
when downloading, serving, or redistributing model artifacts.

Vendored code
-------------

`src/procl/` is a cleaned vendor copy of

  DeepFoldProtein/DeepFold-PLM -> plmMSA/src/procl

originally authored by Hanjin Bae <iwdhanjin@gmail.com>. The upstream project
does not ship procl as a standalone distribution, so the source is committed
in-tree here. Significant edits (formatting, trimmed unused imports, type
hints) have been applied — see git history for the diff.
